    "The proposed SolarNet is dependent on the use of the VMD decomposition algorithm and CNN model.",
    "The input data are; solar radiation, active power data, temperature, and humidity.",
    "The proposed CNN model consists of two structures, max-pooling, and pooling blocks to boost the forecasting effectiveness.",
    "The achieved results show that the proposed model outperforms other deep learning techniques for 1-h ahead forecasting.",
